---

<AdminLayout
  title="Hero"
  description="Hero examples"
  currentPath="front-components/hero"
  enableComponentPreview={true}
>
  <PageHeader {...pageHeaderConfig} />

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-9 order-1 order-lg-0">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <p class="my-0">
            Hero components are prominent sections on websites or applications that introduce users
            to the main message or offering. Typically featuring a bold headline, engaging visuals,
            and a call-to-action, hero blocks aim to grab attention and guide users toward the next
            step or key information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row js-toc-content">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="my-3">
            <h3 class="mb-2" id="example-1">Example 1</h3>

            <ComponentPreview
              title="Hero Example 1"
              height="550px"
              component={code_1}
              htmlCode={code_1}
